- 赴蒞喜晴</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Ph%C3%BA-Th%E1%BB%A9/author-cJyRnXqV8KjQY5jLmb3KOA">Phạm Phú Thứ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Phong-t%E1%BA%ADt-chu-trung-ph%E1%BB%A5c-ch%E1%BA%A9m-th%C6%B0-ho%C3%A0i-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-l%E1%BB%A5c-v%E1%BA%ADn-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-tr%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BB%93-Nam-th%C3%A2n-h%E1%BB%AFu/poem-maRxAMOCboIbSdvxXl781Q">Phong tật chu trung phục chẩm thư hoài tam thập lục vận, phụng trình Hồ Nam thân hữu - 風疾舟中伏枕書懷三十六韻，奉呈湖南親友</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%91ng-T%C3%ADnh-Chi/Thanh-s%C6%A1n-v%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%A5t-%E1%BB%95-%C4%91%E1%BB%93/poem-Ma8QINP2pdUU68iq6YB2Lg">Thanh sơn vân nhất ổ đồ - 青山雲一塢圖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/C%E1%BB%91ng-T%C3%ADnh-Chi/author-ppKojgiwIZGQP9tbBmCpcQ">Cống Tính Chi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/La-Nghi%E1%BB%87p/Thu%E1%BB%B7-li%C3%AAm/poem-O_TcOBdhoUwKPCWIU8W1-w">Thuỷ liêm - 水帘</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/La-Nghi%E1%BB%87p/author-2At56aS2QnIC1468ghv69Q">La Nghiệp</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tr%E1%BB%9F-v%C5%A9-b%E1%BA%A5t-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-quy-Nh%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-T%C3%A2y-cam-l%C3%A2m/poem-M53RSlFcPrFgDdYAitDzcg">Trở vũ bất đắc quy Nhương Tây cam lâm - 阻雨不得歸瀼西甘林</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
